                <mxCell id="16" value="&lt;h1 style=&quot;margin-top: 0px;&quot;&gt;Summary&lt;/h1&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: &amp;quot;Mona Sans VF&amp;quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &amp;quot;Segoe UI&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Noto Sans&amp;quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif, &amp;quot;Apple Color Emoji&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Segoe UI Emoji&amp;quot;; font-size: 16px; white-space: pre-wrap;&quot;&gt;You are a blob of nanobots of a tiny size (between microscopic and golf ball) The goal is to escape the lab by going through walls and other stuff (hence borders) losing mass in the progress. You will need to conserve mass to stay alive and other things that reduce mass include heat spots, electricity, and other nano bot blobs.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;" style="text;html=1;whiteSpace=wrap;overflow=hidden;rounded=0;" vertex="1" parent="1">
